text: San Pablo Nuevo is a corregimiento in David District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 1,752 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 1,192; its population as of 2000 was 1,642. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
